article_text:
BY:



President Obama’s roll call attempt fell short on Tuesday during his speech at MacDill Air Force Base in Tampa, Florida.

Obama got roaring responses from CENTCOM, SOCOM, Army, Navy, and the Marines, but the Coast Guard? Not so much.

“We love our Coast Guard,” Obama said after an awkward silence and some laughter from the military crowd.
